Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三玖 你要说的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要平等 公平就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是在说篝火晚会的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.46,0:00:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班上的人说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说男女必须在晚会结束的瞬间把手牵手在一起才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 风太郎有两只手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两只手各牵一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 我咳嗽了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要滑雪了 回去静养吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我好不容易换好衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 病人就该好好躺着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来症状果然恶化了 我们都不走运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:00:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和风太郎说过自己生病？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开了免提
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三玖和风太郎在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要找到孤单的五月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在应该很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月居然不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始滑雪之后我还一次都没见到她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是去了高难度滑道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你流了好多汗 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没办法继续欺骗自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:01:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是被濑叶传染了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说一花也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是对不起她了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是休息一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现三玖和上杉同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能在这种地方放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一花和二乃也抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就只有五月了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也没找到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我明明也在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一花 都说了让你休息的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我被四叶抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 风太郎和一花都回旅馆休息去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四叶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让五月逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我到处都找过了 没有发现她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情说不定比我想象中的还要严重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇难？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 绕了这么多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都没有发现五月 这太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是联系不上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一花 五月亲口说了要来滑雪的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边好像还没去过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地方 老师之前说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是还没修整好的危险路线 不能进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回旅馆看看她有没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是再找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 实在找不到甚至需要呼叫救援啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月可能也不希望把事情闹大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闹大？说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这关乎五月的生命 别说得这么轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月 你到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风太郎 你还是休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我应该在哪里见…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs42}听得见吗 风太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs42}我和风太郎说过自己生病了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危险 差点就被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我有头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头绪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 应该能找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以相信你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一花 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你说的头绪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要从这里找？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实看得挺清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 那不是五月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们正下方的那个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那人怎么看都是个男的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你眼睛不好 不戴眼镜根本看不清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 把事情搞这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难说出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在刚才发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:05:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫「上杉同学」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一花会叫我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于你们的这些小事 我还是了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到五月了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你眼里风太郎就那么差劲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牵扯上男女关系 那就是另一回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对他一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男性还是仔细观察观察比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月还在观察他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 风太郎和父亲不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想要确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太容易露陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篝火晚会马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请学生到广场集合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先让上杉同学在这里静养观察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 你们去把他的行李拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来陪他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我也留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们留在这里也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己能行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你也太不领情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始这个房间禁止进入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得风太郎喜欢上林间学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他一个人孤零零得结束真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的舞蹈怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs42}我现在就去邀请她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩是不是已经有搭档了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我跳一支舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:08:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 二乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是还兴奋地说你能和男生跳舞来着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被鸽子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像有事分不开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在滑雪场偶然遇到他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他托我给你带个话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是被他讨厌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我会一直等下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二乃 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么 还不快去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 打起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那副模样还好意思说我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是担心下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能相信你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:09:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是火大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去趟厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点的话晚会就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没人和你跳 我就陪你跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你 感冒要多喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有热的抹茶苏打水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧退了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是我把感冒传染给风太郎的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风太郎从一开始就不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想想 他一直身体不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是仔细盯着他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我顾着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该拒绝这场跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是早点发现就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个传说 三玖的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三玖？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一花和二乃 还有其他人都是如何对待风太郎的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得只有我与大家不同 这样不平等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我改变主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要他只属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法欺骗这份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过 现在还不是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢风太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我按自己的想法来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对的 一花和大家也可以按自己的想法来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是超管用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是没装成一花的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四叶 上杉同学的行李还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四叶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是上杉同学的指南
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面贴满了便签 写满了笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来他那么期待林间学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他身体不舒服 我还拉着他到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我让他的林间学校泡汤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我没做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 上杉同学有什么感受 在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去问他 我们根本不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这一切该不会是白费
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给濑叶讲的林间趣闻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在车里的五姐妹玩小游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四叶来帮忙试胆大会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,候补 第三天去滑雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（四叶好像要教我滑雪）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人惊讶的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三玖说他的林间学校结束会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实他很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去问问上杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是直接
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能像四叶那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主任 主任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篝火晚会快结束了 您能来帮下忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您睡着了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然学四叶跑了进来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是在老师睡觉的时候潜入房间也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会太大胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不能让下他一个人在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先开灯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得 开关就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小声点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么会在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比较惊讶二乃竟然会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想给借他一个特别灵的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是担心风太郎才来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都想到一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了我不是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉同学 大家都想让你好点起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我还不了解你是怎么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你醒了 要是你愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我讲讲你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篝火晚会马上就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家一起来倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:15:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 已经到会场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么连那么重要东西都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会拿过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 是风太郎的电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是把婚戒忘在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有这样的新郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有其父必有其子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还有另外一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要比爸爸和哥哥还好的人结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不同意 不要丢下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友呢 你还没男朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥也是一如既往对工作以外的事情很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟学生时代比进步已经很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很担心他能不能成为一个好丈夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 早饭只有这么点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近家庭收支这么紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧张是紧张 但是是其他原因啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在吃太多多可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟今天的午饭超级豪华的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像城堡一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会发生这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 是准备出了问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天要换这么多衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会有穿上的一天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮您挽上头发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道今天有多重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你马上就要结婚了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是哥哥却是一个超级现实的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会在意这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还留着这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜结婚 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新郎 入场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 是我啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别告诉我你不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是前田吧 也恭喜二位了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙还是没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 他也是我们的丘比特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林间学校的传说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真怀念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉他们那时候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的事 说实话我已经记不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不但是 多灾多难的林间学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来似乎也并不是很令人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新娘 入场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结缘的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最后一刻跳舞的男女会白头偕老
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那段青涩的回忆所以让我感受到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是因为有大家陪伴在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候你也一直忍受着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太不注意这方面的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说不像你的话 快变回平时的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们五个人陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的力量恢复精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这次林间学校当中感受到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复精神了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咒语好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 还让不让人睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉同学生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 很精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 说不定我能说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时没能说出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs42}上杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体不要紧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 住院拖下的进度我得赶紧补回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再借你一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.44,0:23:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月你吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上肚子会饿的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.31,0:23:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 为了庆祝风太郎恢复健康
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后一起去车站前买可丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是去学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续教我学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就丢下二乃 其他人一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没说不参加
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 为了期末考试我要严厉点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.38,0:23:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.38,0:23:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好心理准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.19,0:23:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.98,0:24:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃快逃
